 <p class="p" xmlns="">Dr Beard is chief of the Bacterial Diseases Branch, Division of Vector-Borne Diseases, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, Fort Collins, Colorado. His research interests are Lyme disease, plague, tularemia, and the influence of climate on disease ecology.</p>
